{"tid":1109462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心偷食】廉署極速出po抽水：咪以為保密到足 就可以Cheating","createTime":"2019-04-16T09:28:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T20:01:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":50,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9ddf2074d32bef92b00b622f2ed08114c03d213f","tid":1109462,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"歌手許志安，與藝人黃心穎被爆出「偷食」醜聞，當中長達逾15分鐘的片段，疑由車內鏡頭所攝。由廉政公署負責的facebook專頁「全城‧傳誠」，極速以《Cheat精Cheating斷到正》為題發帖「抽水」，在配圖、內文和hashtag呼籲網民「咪以為保密功夫做到足，就可以Cheating；數碼足跡、天眼到處都係，要搵貪污證據，其實唔難，邊有咁易走得甩？」、「咪以為黑蚊蚊冇人知，做過梗有痕迹」、「#教而不善」、「#教而不善 #收授雙方一齊玩完 #貪心邊有得咁安心 #要學識制服心魔同誘惑 #現實離奇過劇集」，可謂語帶雙關。<br />\n<br />\n廉署抽水全文<br />\n【Cheat精Cheating斷到正】咪以為保密功夫做到足就可以Cheating，數碼足跡、天眼到處都係，要搵貪污證據，其實唔難，邊有咁易走得甩？<br />\n#正Cheat精 #Cheating #人太貪婪心盲無明 #貪念是一條大坑會坑掉人的哦 #SoSad #教而不善 #收授雙方一齊玩完 #貪心邊有得咁安心 #要學識制服心魔同誘惑 #現實離奇過劇集 #全城傳誠 #AllforIntegrity #ICAC<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190416/large/1555404987_c8ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190416%2Flarge%2F1555404987_c8ee.png&h=ee4bef29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190416/59495373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190416%2F59495373&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FMxSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=b299fd5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190416%2F59495373&h=3a4e951e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190416/59495373</a>"},{"pid":"e5cbe338d3fadac7d86fde1c7d5b792d5655fd50","tid":1109462,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"308247c3f175d6906735dec1a814de7be06177a8","tid":1109462,"uid":52942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-1